      "description": "FEA ensemble predictions for construct stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement were compared against N=6 quasi-static ASTM F1717 tests conducted at Laboratory A (MTS 858 Mini Bionix, displacement rate 5 mm/min, ambient temperature 23±2 °C). All three QoIs fell within the 10% acceptance band; E/uval ranged from 0.41 to 1.12, satisfying the E/uval < 1.96 criterion.",
