      "description": "FEA ensemble predictions were compared against N=5 quasi-static ASTM F1717 tests conducted at Laboratory B (Instron 5967, displacement rate 5 mm/min). Inter-laboratory variability in yield force was 3.8%; FEA fell within this band. E/uval = 1.31 for yield force, the highest observed metric across both labs, still satisfying the acceptance criterion.",
      "comparedAgainst": "https://uofa.net/synth/data/lab-b-quasi-static-n5",
